     C/EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      ** VALIDATION - Risk Weighting Code
      *****************************************************************
     C     RWCDV         BEGSR
 
      * If risk weighting code is entered, must be on file
     C     DDRWCD        IFNE      *BLANK
     C     DDRWCD        CHAIN     CUSRSKWT                           90
     C     *IN90         IFEQ      '1'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           DDRWCDOK
     C                   ADD       1             Idx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDRWCD'      FldNamXAr(Idx)
     C                   MOVEL     'USR1459'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)
     C                   ENDIF
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      *
     C                   ENDSR
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      * *INZSR - Program Initialisation routine                       *
      *****************************************************************
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      *
      * INPUTS
      *
      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeOut
      *
      ** Risk Weighting Code (4A)
     C                   PARM                    DDRWCD            4
      *
      * OUTPUTS
      *
      * Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Risk Weighting Code - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDRWCDOK          1
